NAME
    lorem-tickit - Tickit application with lorem ipsum generator.

SYNOPSIS
     lorem-tickit [-h] [--version]

DESCRIPTION
    This application is an interactive Tickit lorem ipsum generator.

ARGUMENTS
    *       "-h"

            Print help.

    *       "--version"

            Print version of script.

CONTROLS
    *       "Tab", arrows

            Select setting.

    *       "+", "-"

            Increase or decrease selected count.

    *       "Enter", "Space"

            Use selected generator.

    *       "q"

            Quit.

REPOSITORY
    <https://github.com/michal-josef-spacek/App-Lorem-Tickit>

SEE ALSO
    Lorem <https://flathub.org/en/apps/org.gnome.design.Lorem>
        Simple app to generate the well-known Lorem Ipsum placeholder text.

